text:
Am I supposed to wear this?
Me? Alone?

Yeah...
Is there something bothering you?

Well,
it's not so much that...

If it was for Houkura, it'd be fine,
but I don't have the courage to wear this alone...

Really? I think it's a good outfit
that brings out Juri's charm.

My charm...
You're not just saying that, right...?

Specifically, I believe this outfit will enhance
Juri's cuteness and coolness even more...

O-Okay...
I got it, I got it...

I understand your feelings! So please, spare me the
embarrassment of saying embarrassing things directly...
